C O D E X 
P R E S E N T S 



Star Control: Origins (c) Stardock Entertainment 


Release Date : 09/2018 Protection : Steam 
Discs : 1 Genre : Action 



Welcome to Star Control, Captain! Youre here because youve shown 
exemplary service, aced all your flight exams, and - most 
importantly - passed all the sanity tests. Humanity has learned 
that it is not alone in the universe and that we are hopelessly 
outmatched by alien civilizations seeking to destroy us. You have 
been selected to command Earth's first and only interstellar 
starship to accomplish this - try not to break it
